{"tid":1217040,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"借神槍手事件借刀 女事主慘被屈","createTime":"2019-06-13T11:47:06.000Z","updateTime":"2019-06-13T12:09:41.000Z","uid":216555,"like":3,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"a4cd3622913fa148954c745cad067037a56d8bd8","tid":1217040,"uid":216555,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-13T11:47:06.000Z","msg":"石妺<br />\n 😭跪求大家幫我澄清！<br />\n<br />\n我就係相片中 嘅當事人！<br />\n<br />\n認識我嘅朋友都知道我嘅背景！<br />\n<br />\n 亦都清楚明白知道😔<br />\n我係一個單親媽媽湊住三個小朋友！<br />\n<br />\n我亦都很請認識我嘅人幫我澄清😫<br />\n<br />\n我亦都知道邊一個 做呢件事嚟騷擾我💢<br />\n<br />\n🚓我上個禮拜已經報咗&mdash;次警！<br />\n📌由於係因為工作上嘅關係 問題，所以佢騷擾咗我兩個星期！ 成件事我亦都有證據證明唔係我問題<br />\n📌( 亦都可能有人個別覺得 係我錯啩,，但係十個有11個都話唔係我問題)📌<br />\n<br />\n本身我都因為屋企問題精神壓力過大要睇醫生！ 我亦都因為呢件事畀佢騷擾過度瞓唔到覺 我每日淨係瞓得嗰兩個鐘💤加埋都唔知有冇😔<br />\n<br />\n我亦都因為呢件事而自殘兩次💊<br />\n食安眠藥三十幾粒兩晚加埋應該有七十幾粒再加飲酒😔<br />\n我講出嚟唔係要大家同情 我係想大家 評理！ <br />\n<br />\n😠因為報警求助無門😠<br />\n希望大家幫我平反❗<br />\n<br />\n我有電話紀錄證明，佢可以搵人一日12個鐘☎️打咗最少600個電話畀我!<br />\n<br />\n因為警察話冇實質證據所以 做唔到嘢！<br />\n 本身我都冇諗住公開佢嘅事情 同個人資料facebook！<br />\n但今次影響我 同啲小朋友 人生安全我覺得！<br />\n所以我要澄清！ 我好驚萬一出街有人會對我同啲小朋友唔知做啲咩！<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Neo6eC8.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FNeo6eC8.png&h=ad3dbde2&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/8BFPWRu.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F8BFPWRu.png&h=294166a5&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/6NnbqKQ.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F6NnbqKQ.png&h=29473e14&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/gEwvGib.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FgEwvGib.png&h=39bcc7bc&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/DzJxUDc.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FDzJxUDc.png&h=ec0f8af6&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/jskXmic.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FjskXmic.png&h=60f7123e&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/GiPdD4T.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FGiPdD4T.png&h=6ca745cf&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/KNE5vbz.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FKNE5vbz.png&h=24661bda&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/k0z5vbA.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fk0z5vbA.png&h=170af568&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/PwdYQbB.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FPwdYQbB.png&h=aff33895&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"2288b5f406af334b341f7f41a5b91afa370c3fc7","tid":1217040,"uid":216555,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-13T11:48:48.000Z","msg":"Up"},{"pid":"f3c60e048193fd80142f044c2dd6c3c4afe5ff86","tid":1217040,"uid":216555,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-13T11:54:41.000Z","msg":"推 以後小心借刀"},{"pid":"b6fa91424b6d194d72760bbc41159c22469acc67","tid":1217040,"uid":236414,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-13T11:56:23.000Z","msg":"今時今日要借刀超級易，<br />\n屈仇人做黑警條女就得"},{"pid":"ca690b31f3d89668dd1a34546d6495a4904b9108","tid":1217040,"uid":216555,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-13T12:09:41.000Z","msg":"Up"}]}